    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey everyone! \ud83d\udc4b I\u2019m honestly so sad to let this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for someone else to enjoy it! It is in absolutely pristine, showroom condition\u2014honestly, you\u2019d think it just rolled off the assembly line yesterday. I\u2019ve babied this car from day one, keeping it spotless and strictly following every maintenance schedule. It drives like a dream and still has that 'new car' feel. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s practically perfect, this is definitely the one! Come take a look and fall in love! \u2728",
      "price": 44500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
