      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 23
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering an investment-grade E46 M3, a pinnacle of atmospheric engineering. This example features the S54 3.2L inline-six, renowned for its 8,000 RPM redline and individual throttle bodies. The mechanical provenance is impeccable: the high-pressure VANOS system has been overhauled, and the connecting rod bearings have been replaced with treated shells for long-term reliability. The chassis is structurally perfect, with a proactively reinforced rear subframe to maintain torsional rigidity. Power is delivered through a precise Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox to a factory limited-slip differential. Every suspension pivot utilizes fresh bushings, and the damping remains tight, mirroring original factory delivery specifications. The exterior retains its deep luster with zero evidence of oxidation or panel misalignment, while the cabin's Nappa leather remains supple and free of bolster deformation.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 23
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "2022 Model S. Single owner. Garage kept. Zero scratches or dents. Original paint. Smoke-free interior. Full service history included.",
      "price": 43000.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 23
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is a true time capsule, maintained to a standard rarely seen outside of a showroom. The exterior retains its deep, mirror-like factory luster with zero rock chips or swirl marks, protected by a professional ceramic coating. Inside, the cabin remains pristine; the premium leather seats show no bolster wear, and the original floor mats are spotless. Mechanically, it is flawless, benefiting from a documented history of preventative maintenance and recent fluid services. Always stored in a climate-controlled garage and never driven in inclement weather, this car offers the tactile feel and reliability of a brand-new vehicle. Every button, switch, and feature operates exactly as intended. If you are looking for an investment-grade example that requires absolutely zero apologies, this is it.",
      "price": 43900.0,
